{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/669810.Jeaniene_Frost", "name": "Jeaniene Frost", "genres": ["Romance", "Science Fiction & Fantasy", "Paranormal"], "avg_rating": 4.21, "num_reviews": 43680, "num_ratings": 823301, "about": "Jeaniene Frost is the New York Times, USA Today, and international bestselling author of the Night Huntress series, the Night Prince series, the Broken Destiny series, and the upcoming Night Rebel series. To date, foreign rights for her novels have sold to twenty different countries. Jeaniene lives in Florida with her husband Matthew, who long ago accepted that she rarely cooks and always sleeps in on the weekends. Aside from writing, Jeaniene enjoys reading, poetry, watching movies with her husband, exploring old cemeteries, spelunking and traveling \u2013 by car. Airplanes, children, and cook books frighten her.For information on Jeaniene's books, book trailers, deleted scenes, creature mythology, and more, please visit: www.jeanienefrost.com"}
