{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/13084.Roland_Barthes", "name": "Roland Barthes", "birth_date": "1915-11-12 00:00:00", "death_date": "1980-03-26 00:00:00", "genres": ["Art", "Literature & Fiction", "Philosophy"], "influences": [" Friedrich Nietzsche", " Jean-Paul Sartre", " Geo", " Georges Bataille", " Jules Michelet", " Karl Marx", " Ferdinand de Saussure", " Paul Val\u00e9ry", " Jacques Lacan", " Sigmund Freud"], "avg_rating": 4.01, "num_reviews": 2817, "num_ratings": 80563, "about": "Roland G\u00e9rard Barthes was a French literary theorist, philosopher, linguist, critic, and semiotician. Barthes' ideas explored a diverse range of fields and he influenced the development of schools of theory including structuralism, semiotics, social theory, design theory, anthropology, and post-structuralism."}
