{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/339564.Martin_Fletcher", "name": "Martin Fletcher", "genres": ["Thriller", "Memoir", "Historical Fiction"], "avg_rating": 3.8, "num_reviews": 559, "num_ratings": 3768, "about": "MARTIN FLETCHER is one of the most respected television news correspondents in the world and he is also rapidly gaining an equally impressive reputation as a writer. He has won many awards, including five Emmys, a Columbia University DuPont Award, several Overseas Press Club Awards, and the National Jewish Book Award. Fletcher and his wife, Hagar, have raised three sons. He spent many years as the NBC News Bureau Chief in Tel Aviv and he is currently based in Israel and New York, where he is a Special Correspondent for NBC News. He is also the author of Breaking News, Walking Israel, The List, Jacob's Oath, The War Reporter and Promised Land."}
