ndon). This book is a long time best seller. It sells over 20,000 copies in paper per year in the US alone. The digital version sells twice that. THE NEW ASTROLOGY\u2122 also exists and sells well in British English, French, German, Dutch, Spanish, Polish and Czech. 3) 1992 THE NEW CHINESE ASTROLOGY - Macmillan ...more"}
