es that have made a measurable difference to quality of his life and will for yours as well.Topics that George M. Posi write about are: Health and Fitness, Yoga, Mind and Beliefs, Emotions, Relationship, Mission and Purpose, Productivity, Spirituality, and more... ...more"}
