{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/14195702.A_M_Manay", "name": "A.M. Manay", "genres": ["Fantasy", "Thriller", "Paranormal"], "avg_rating": 4.57, "num_reviews": 124, "num_ratings": 268, "about": "In addition to her work as an indie author of paranormal new adult fantasy, A.M. Manay is a former inner-city chemistry teacher, a singer, a yoga enthusiast, a Clerk of Session in the Presbyterian Church (USA), and a mother through domestic open adoption. She has a passion for increasing diversity in popular culture and for strong heroines who stand up for themselves, make their own decisions, and don't depend on romance as their reason for being."}
