{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/200710.Christopher_Duggan", "name": "Christopher Duggan", "birth_date": "1957-11-04 00:00:00", "death_date": "2015-11-02 00:00:00", "genres": ["Biography", "Italian History"], "influences": ["Denis Mack Smith"], "avg_rating": 3.79, "num_reviews": 54, "num_ratings": 461, "about": "Christopher John Hesketh Duggan was a British historian specialising in the political, social and cultural history of modern Italy. He began his career as a research fellow at Wolfson College, Oxford and then at All Souls College, Oxford. In 1987, he moved to the University of Reading where he remained until his death. He had been Professor of Modern Italian History since 2002."}
