{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/410418.Susane_Colasanti", "name": "Susane Colasanti", "genres": ["Romance", "Contemporary", "Young Adult"], "avg_rating": 3.74, "num_reviews": 7042, "num_ratings": 118327, "about": "Susane Colasanti is the bestselling author of When It Happens, Take Me There, Waiting for You, Something Like Fate, So Much Closer, Keep Holding On, All I Need, Now and Forever, the City Love trilogy, and the serial fiction book Inside Wants Out. She has a bachelor\u2019s degree from the University of Pennsylvania and a master\u2019s degree from New York University. Before becoming a full-time author in 2007, Susane was a high school science teacher for ten years. She lives in New York City. You can connect with Susane on her Facebook, Twitter, YouTube, Tumblr, and Instagram."}
