{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/2752627.Susannah_Appelbaum", "name": "Susannah Appelbaum", "genres": ["Fantasy", "Horror", "Young Adult"], "avg_rating": 3.6, "num_reviews": 100, "num_ratings": 737, "about": "Susannah Appelbaum realized at an early age that the world contains both good and evil\u2014and she wanted nothing more than to write about it. By day, she does so. The night is reserved for keeping the world safe from shadows and demons. She has lived both in Paris and at the Carlyle hotel, where the service is exquisite and the food is never burnt. Susannah resides in New York\u2019s Hudson Valley and is the critically acclaimed author of the Poisons of Caux series."}
